data.description: Back on the market in time for the holidays! Now's your chance to own this wonderful home! Welcome to 10804 Middleboro Drive in Spring Garden Estates. This gorgeous single family home in the sought-after Damascus school cluster is waiting for you! With 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths and a one-car garage, it has everything you could want.  The upper level has hardwood floors throughout and features an updated kitchen and an open concept living/dining room—perfect for cooking and entertaining. The giant sunroom is the star of the show! Bright and open with its wall of windows, it provides a warm and welcoming space that could be an office, playroom, or extra dining space—you name it! Also on the upper level is the primary suite with a full bath, dressing area and a sliding barn door leading to the walk-in closet. Plus, two more good-sized bedrooms share a newly renovated full bath. Host your next movie night or watch the big game in the huge family room on the lower level. New carpet and a wood burning fireplace make a cozy spot for friends and family. Also on the lower level are the fourth bedroom and a newly renovated full bath. Plus, there’s a bonus room, laundry with tons of storage and walk-out access to the garage. Other features include brand new roof (July 2023), extra parking pad on the driveway, newer kitchen appliances (2019), AC (2011), energy efficient windows (2010), AND NO HOA! Close to Magruder Branch Trail for hiking and biking, Damascus Community Center and even Jimmie Cone all while in one of the best school districts in MoCo! Shopping, restaurants, and retail stores are nearby in Damascus, Mount Airy and Clarksburg Outlets. Don’t miss this opportunity! Make your appointment today!
